	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">En tandem <persName ref="p4544" cert="high">Ciceronis</persName>, quem petisti, librum, et ago gratias de novis mihi communicatis.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quid <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l41" cert="high">Bernę</placeName> sit actum et adhuc agatur cum <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p3099">Sulcerianis</persName>, fortassis melius nosti quam ego.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Articulos vidi et legi, quos volebant nescio quo spiritu proponere pastoribus ad excutiendum <note type="misc">[korr. - endos]</note>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2464" cert="high">Gallica</placeName> ingenia multum hactenus evangelio incommodarunt; habent perpetuo quaestiones innumerabiles.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ecclesia nostra fere adobruitur novis istis hominibus.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vos feliciores estis, qui talibus caretis hominibus, quorum fides nobis incognita, quorum conversatio hypocritica est sique nobis imponunt specie probitatis.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Dissidium inter episcopos et principes <placeName ref="l18" cert="high">Augustę</placeName> ortum te clam esse non reor; quę autem ignoras, <persName ref="p8418" cert="high">Myconius</persName> narrat in sua epistola.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Hoc autem scio <persName ref="p467" cert="high">Bucerum</persName> periclitatum fuisse et tentatum variis modis.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Iam Moguntinę liber a <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p18538" cert="high">Caesare</persName> mittendus concordiam ecclesiarum <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2498" cert="high">Germanicarum</placeName> continens excuditur; nam papyrus paratur, characteres ornantur, et expectat typographus in singulas horas librum, quem <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l875" cert="high">Hispani</placeName> et monachi <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2498" cert="high">Germanici</placeName>, <persName type="auto_name">Wicelus Flugius</persName> excuderunt <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p18538" cert="high">Caesare</persName> iubente.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Episcopi furiunt contra hoc Caesaris statutum.</s>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Dominus autem novit, quid sit facturus in religione, quę ipsius gloriam plantatura est et ebuccinatura, in cuius manu corda sunt regum.</s>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l492" cert="high">Argentina</placeName> quotidie habet <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l875" cert="high">Hispanicos</placeName> et <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l994" cert="high">Neapolitanos</placeName> milites, quos honorifice excipiunt.</s>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Passim in marchionatu <persName type="auto_name">Ernesti</persName> et <persName type="citizen_name">baronis de Hanou</persName>, item episcopi <placeName ref="l492" cert="high">Argentoratensis</placeName> militibus obruuntur, qui depascunt omnia.</s>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Pęnam dignam luit episcopus; si vult, ut milites relinquant suos pagos, cogitur dare pecuniae summam.</s>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Dann man ist den knechten schuldig zwen monat soldts; so das capitel mit dem bischoff sy bezalt, so wellen sy hinweg ziegen uff ein anderen bischoff oder apt, der feist ist und vil gelts hat, den müssen sy ouch uß fressen.</s>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><foreign xml:lang="de">Also schuldig und unschuldig, bischoff und bader, muͦß sich liden;</foreign> nulla differentia inter pium et impium, etsi nebulones isti digni sint maiore pęna ob idololatriam, quam fovent et defendunt ad insaniam usque.</s>
					<s n="18" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Verum heus tu, novum concionatorem habemus <placeName ref="l28" cert="high">Basileę</placeName>, qui novum evangelium, ut vulgus loquitur, divulgat.</s>
					<s n="19" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Currit turba populi ad illum; non credis, qualem ex plebe habeat frequentiam.</s>
					<s n="20" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Timeo, ne tandem comędia illa in tragędiam vertatur; nam novi vulgi inconstantiam, novi etiam quorundam ingenia, qui solent etiam bonis viris abuti pulchra specie.</s>
					<s n="21" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Dominus det nobis tranquillitatem et prudentiam, ne insipienter in vocandis ministris agamus!</s>
					<s n="22" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tu nosti <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8184" cert="high">Valentinum</persName><note xml:id="fn1" type="footnote" n="1"><persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8184" cert="high">Boltz</persName>.</note>, qui fortassis ex agro vestro ad nos venit; bonus est vir et mihi familiaris, sed turbat et invidia gravat ministros reliquos...</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note>[Schluss; Autograph: Zürich StA, E II 366, 186 (Siegel...)]</note>
					<s n="23" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quę subsecutura sunt, bene intelliges.</s>
					<s n="24" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="farewell">Vale, et si quid habes novi, velis communicare <persName ref="p1278" cert="high">Gastio</persName> tuo, qui tibi et omnibus <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l587" cert="high">Tigurinis</placeName> bene vult et cupit.</s>
					<s n="25" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Neque hoc praeterire debeo: <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l1325" cert="high">Jenae</placeName> scholam publicam erigere principes <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l749" cert="high">Saxonię</placeName> tristes volunt; sed <persName ref="p2095" cert="high">Philippus Melanchthon</persName> suam operam illis denegat; vult <placeName ref="l558" cert="high">Witembergę</placeName> manere.</s>
					<s n="26" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Qui fit?</s>
					<s n="27" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Habet pulchras ędes, hortum, prata.</s>
					<s n="28" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName ref="p4443" cert="high">Pomeranus</persName> dicit se senem esse.</s>
					<s n="29" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quid si <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2510" cert="high">Turca</placeName> veniret, an mansuri essent et negaturi fidem aut <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p18593" cert="high">Turcarum</persName> religionem approbaturi?</s>
					<s n="30" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Miseri homines.</s>
					<s n="31" xml:lang="la" type="auto">8. maii 1548.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="32" xml:lang="la" type="auto">T(uus) <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p1278" cert="high">G(astius)</persName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="33" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Raptim.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note type="address">[Adresse:]</note>
					<s n="34" xml:lang="la" type="auto">D. <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p495" cert="high">Heinrycho Bullingero</persName>, amico suo syncero etc.</s>
					<s n="35" xml:lang="de" type="auto"><placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l587" cert="high">Zürich</placeName></s>
				</p>
			</div>
